>廣東河源雅居樂三期一幢在建住宅樓倒塌，鋼筋斷裂，灰塵彌漫，數秒鐘之內整幢樓被夷為平地。影片顯示事發於周一下午，涉及面積約5,000平方米。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據現場一名民工稱，正常的樓盤地盤一般拆模板都是20多天才拆卸，他在雅居樂這邊施工不到10天就拆了，有可能是樓房樁柱不牢固、樓板受力太大引發倒塌的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果 Link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56016190&amp;amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;amp;category=instant&amp;amp;issue=20161207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56016190%26amp%3Bcategory_guid%3D10793096%26amp%3Bcategory%3Dinstant%26amp%3Bissue%3D20161207&d=Qd%2Fxl2lbfmvJlqhRLJU89ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=98dac363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56016190%26amp%3Bcategory_guid%3D10793096%26amp%3Bcategory%3Dinstant%26amp%3Bissue%3D20161207&h=b1ecafda\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56016190&amp;amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;amp;category=instant&amp;amp;issue=20161207</a></blockquote><br />\n河源市雅居樂房地產中心今日指網傳圖片及影片不實，事件起因為拆除一幢違規建築，屬於正常拆建，「雅居樂房地產每季度有建築質量檢測，檢測之後發現建築局部不符合公司的建設標準，要求施工方拆除再建，沒有出現人員傷亡情況。」河源當地警方及急救中心今日覆稱，周一並未接獲相關報案電話。<br />\n<br />\n拆完又起起完又拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3286ca59f3020983a2eecdf99d52d7e39248ec0","tid":27400,"uid":19982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"瓦居礫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2191d9bb1a84e766c5c3e44ee2dfa5b16fd6263","tid":27400,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"死港燦買大陸樓禁撚威威丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe067726263ccb03f6b03a56ff44bc51a5320a59","tid":27400,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Miniature<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 勿跟车太贴</blockquote><br />\n屌你老